notes: one adjective and one noun are chosen at random. If this is impossible to make work in a language, then just change the format to say "The Cats", or make the adjectives empty and randomize some teamnames in the Noun slots
if the adjective is prepended with "format2|" then the team name will use this format instead of the default one
if more than 2 formats are needed for a language, I can add more (just let me know).

nouns may be prepended with the text "singular|" (ex if the noun is Team or Sqaud instead of Cats). This changes the grammar in the embark/return/fail cutscenes (ex: "{Teamname} Returns Home" vs {Teamname} Return Home")
these do not need to be strictly literal translations, you can be creative with them
